snippet.textDisplay: I must admit I never before understood the danger of identity politics until this channel showed up in my feed and I watched a few videos. I am all for diversity and inclusion across the spectrums of gender and race and identity, but the irony of this channel is they are playing up our differences in very demeaning, simplistic and inappropriate ways, breaking us all down into categories and tribes, all while doing it with a smile and pretending to celebrate our differences. You can't judge a book by it's cover, folks, and these people would be ashamed for doing so.

snippet.textDisplay: For any kids and teenagers reading the comments.... EDUCATION IS IMPORTANT! Don’t let people tell you school is stupid. Get your GED/Diploma. Go on to something you love. Whether it’s college, a trade school, cosmetology school, the military, tattooing, or literally anything. Try your hardest and don’t say education is stupid, because it’s not. Your greatest asset in life is your brain, so use it. You don’t have to get a college degree to be successful, definitely not, but try for that high school level education. It’ll set you up in life.
